**Overview**
This dashboard is designed to offer comprehensive statistics and display the ingested logs related to audit activities from Sublime Security.

The dashboard provides an overview of events over time and highlights the top 10 source IPs and email addresses involved in audit activities.

It shows a breakdown of activities by user roles, event types, and authentication methods.

[**Integrations Page**](/app/integrations/detail/sublime_security-0.1.0/overview)
